oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Liberty Street in Jackson
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: “N. on Liberty St. from Baltimore. -- Jackson, Tenn.” Black-and-white image of street with buildings, including Business College.

“Miss Olive Cormeable -- 148 Stewart Av -- Jackson, -- Mich -- Miss Cormeablet was -- glad to hear from -- you. Would have -- answered sooner -- but have been -- in Jackson Tenn -- most of the -- week. Quite a -- coincidence isn’t -- it. Everything lovely -- By PA Train”
